{"text_id":20473,"tokens":["Quantum"," chess"," is"," a"," version"," of"," regular"," chess"," that"," incorporates"," the"," quantum"," concepts"," of"," superposition",","," entanglement",","," and"," interference","."," The"," game"," teaches"," players"," to"," develop"," an"," intuitive"," sense"," of"," the"," rules"," of"," quantum"," mechanics","."," The"," game"," is"," played"," on"," a"," standard"," chess"," board"," with"," standard"," chess"," pieces","."," However",","," each"," piece"," is"," also"," assigned"," a"," quantum"," state",","," which"," can"," be"," one"," of"," two"," possible"," values"," (","up"," or"," down",","," for"," example",")."," The"," player"," can"," choose"," to"," place"," the"," piece"," in"," either"," state",","," but"," once"," it"," is"," placed",","," the"," state"," is"," fixed","."," The"," player"," can"," also"," choose"," to"," ent","angle"," two"," pieces",","," so"," that"," their"," states"," are"," linked","."," This"," means"," that"," if"," one"," piece"," is"," in"," the"," up"," state",","," the"," other"," must"," be"," in"," the"," down"," state"," (","and"," vice"," versa",")."," Ent","angled"," pieces"," cannot"," be"," moved"," independently","."," The"," goal"," of"," the"," game"," is"," to"," check","mate"," the"," opponent","'","s"," king",","," as"," in"," regular"," chess","."," However",","," because"," of"," the"," quantum"," rules"," of"," superposition"," and"," interference",","," it"," is"," possible"," for"," a"," player"," to"," check","mate"," the"," opponent","'","s"," king"," even"," if"," the"," player","'","s"," own"," king"," is"," in"," check","."],"sub_source":"tldr","model":"text-davinci-002","label":1}